                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10207" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2578</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">207 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昔揽众业，今归本心——奥飞娱乐突围之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昔揽众业，今归本心——奥飞娱乐突围之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苗淑娟，郑婷婷，马小棠，彭伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥飞娱乐股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">动漫文化；多元化战略；战略调整；价值内核。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Animation Culture; Diversification Strategy; Strategic Adjustment; Value Kernel.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥飞娱乐作为中国动漫产业的领军企业，从一家小小的玩具作坊起步，历经挑战与机遇，最终成长为覆盖全产业链、规模最大的动漫文化集团，其轨迹映射了中国动漫产业的兴起与变迁。然而在其发展过程中，公司也经历过迷茫：从2013年开始，公司决心发展泛娱乐文化产业，通过并购和跨界布局实现多元化发展，但因资源分散导致经营压力，暴露出一系列风险。随后企业启动动态调适机制，进行战略调整，聚焦核心业务，推动IP创新与智能化发展，探索新的增长路径。本案例选取奥飞娱乐三十余年发展历程，了解企业选择多元化战略的原因、实施多元化战略遇到的问题和战略调整的具体措施，理解企业多元化战略产生的风险以及聚焦价值内核的战略逻辑，为其他公司的战略管理活动提供借鉴。通过本案例，学生可以深入了解多元化战略，理解多元化战略需与企业资源禀赋、核心能力动态适配，并思考动漫产业的未来发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leading enterprise in China&#39;s animation industry, Alpha Group started from a small toy workshop, went through challenges and opportunities, and eventually grew into the largest animation culture group covering the whole industry chain, whose trajectory maps the rise and change of China&#39;s animation industry. However, during its development, the company has also experienced confusion: since 2013, the company is determined to develop the pan-entertainment and culture industry, and realize diversified development through mergers and acquisitions and cross-border layout, but a series of risks have been exposed due to the operational pressure caused by the dispersion of resources. Subsequently, the company launched a dynamic adjustment mechanism to make strategic adjustments, focus on its core business, promote IP innovation and intelligent development, and explore new growth paths. This case selects the development history of Alpha Group for more than 30 years to understand the reasons for the enterprise to choose diversification strategy, the problems encountered in the implementation of diversification strategy and the specific measures for strategic adjustment, to understand the risks arising from the enterprise&#39;s diversification strategy and the strategic logic of focusing on the core of value, and to provide a reference for the strategic management activities of other companies.Through this case study, students can gain a deeper understanding of diversification strategies, comprehend the need for dynamic alignment between diversification strategies and a company&#39;s resource endowments and core competencies, and contemplate the future development of the animation industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">动态能力理论；资源基础理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
